      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_0dc80c7db501aef06c0c386e895e96ba">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged chronologically.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <bioghist id="aspace_b0ad7f36763931a6600072f21cf51316">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>The Yale Medical Journal, a Yale student publication, was established in 1894.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_0b93524e979391ccdc184922a3ee0104">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of the constitution, amendments to the constitution, reports, correspondence, minutes, and journals documenting the activities and operations of the Yale Medical Journal.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
